08:06.353 --> 08:07.953
You're never
supposed to give in.

08:07.955 --> 08:09.621
These things can get
hella intense.

08:09.623 --> 08:11.089
No, no, no, no. At least
let me carry the wheel.

08:11.091 --> 08:12.290
Oh, no.
Let me carry your jacket.

08:12.292 --> 08:13.792
Well, I'm wearing my jacket.

08:13.794 --> 08:15.460
