08:33.113 --> 08:36.348
and hold on to your seat
cushions until I say 'brace.'"

08:36.350 --> 08:37.349
Awesome! Cool!

08:37.351 --> 08:38.717
You were warning them

08:38.719 --> 08:40.352
'cause you're the president
of the plane!

08:40.354 --> 08:41.653
That's right, baby.

08:41.655 --> 08:43.722
So, uh, Gene,
I hope you're hungry,

08:43.724 --> 08:46.491
because we're treating you to a
nice meal at Cattleman's Ranch.

08:46.493 --> 08:49.060
Isn't your family bored
of eating at your restaurant?

08:49.062 --> 08:50.562
Yes, we are! I'm so
tired of the menu.

08:50.564 --> 08:52.397
The portion size is so small.

08:52.399 --> 08:55.967
We got to celebrate, baby!
I've overcome so much.

08:55.969 --> 08:59.471
Took me a while, but my life
is finally on the right track,

08:59.473 --> 09:01.740
which is why
I made us a reservation

09:01.742 --> 09:04.576
at the best restaurant
in Orlando.

09:04.578 --> 09:06.011
