10:39.339 --> 10:41.439
(laughs)

10:41.441 --> 10:43.008
To celebrate,
you should order more food.

10:43.010 --> 10:45.176
What do you have that is $200?

10:45.178 --> 10:46.177
Nothing.

10:46.179 --> 10:48.113
Well, think.

10:48.115 --> 10:50.015
Excuse me.
Where is the bathroom?

10:50.017 --> 10:51.216
Yeah. Right here.

10:53.253 --> 10:56.087
I'll pay the bill.

10:56.089 --> 10:58.156
(indistinct conversations)

